I put her in my Edh deck as card 101 only to sit in the box and watch good cards get played. 4 out of 5 for being a hot cheerleader.  

Seriously though. She doesn't cut it for most token selesnya Edh decks because she is overshadowed by avacyn and eldrazi monument. I honestly can't think of a reason to sub Rhys the redeemed for her like the article talked about.  

@Silence9: she is plain and simply not good even as a commander. Even with token production there is little chance you can keep up with a dedicated token Edh deck ran by a solid general.
